      "title": "Anisotropic Gevrey-Hörmander pseudo-differential operators on modulation spaces",
      "abstract": "We show continuity properties for the pseudo-differential operator $\\operatorname{Op} (a)$ from $M(\\omega _0\\omega ,\\mathscr B )$ to $M(\\omega ,\\mathscr B )$, for fixed $s,\\sigma \\ge 1$, $\\omega ,\\omega _0\\in \\mathscr P _{s,\\sigma}^0$ ($\\omega ,\\omega _0\\in \\mathscr P _{s,\\sigma}$), $a\\in \\Gamma ^{\\sigma,s}_{(\\omega _0)}$ ($a\\in \\Gamma ^{\\sigma,s;0}_{(\\omega _0)}$) , and $\\mathscr B$ is an invariant Banach function space."
